{"type": "article", "id": 51736, "title": "一物多用的镜子，或许能解决空间狭小难题｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-02T23:05:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 48920, "name": "Woud"}, {"id": 48921, "name": "XYZ integrated architecture"}, {"id": 48922, "name": "One Rise East"}, {"id": 48923, "name": "Rikke Frost"}, {"id": 48924, "name": "Sonia Pedrazzini"}, {"id": 48925, "name": "Anna Thorunn"}, {"id": 27335, "name": "Michele de Lucchi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 151, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180402211803UMCpKB3Z6TOSgexi.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #a4a1a1; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #a4a1a1} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>A to Z of Britain 10 pence coins by One Rise East</h3><p>英国皇家铸币局最近发布了一套 26 个 10 便士硬币，从 A 到 Z，展示现代英国文化，操刀这一系列硬币设计的是 One Rise East 事务所。硬币中不乏一些典型的英国元素，比如双层巴士、半球、茶叶以及斑马线。</p><p>但设计团队认为这似乎有些审美疲劳、过时，他们也加入了一些更呼应当代文化的元素，比如 BBC 长篇肥皂剧《伦敦东区》（EastEnders）的主演 Danny Dyer 代表 D，纪录片导演 Louis Theroux 代表 L，歌手 David Bowie 发行的专辑《Ziggy Stardust》代表 Z 等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834PMqkFxya5fCAc47n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834Wo2QVngfxR1aS5GD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834AX8BIb0yFQNvW6D9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834ZDGHigRw1xMYI90B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834BW4DrzMho6jlp7G8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834C3VASX9iPRUHdsKc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211834MvkFYRbAmNuXiaSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/04/02/one-rise-east-royal-mint-a-to-z-britain-coins-alternatives/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Stillness series by Anna Thorunn</h3><p>在冰岛的 2018 DesignMarch 设计节期间，本土设计师 Anna Thorunn 展出了 Stillness 系列，包括折叠式餐具小几、高架托盘桌以及两个烛台。每个作品都以圆形图案为基础构造，她将其描述为“宇宙的象征”。</p><p>高架托盘桌由黑色粉末涂层钢制成，它有一个由三条腿支撑的浅圆形托盘，另有一个垂直于其表面的圆形装饰手柄。较小的托盘桌则没有装饰性手柄。烛台由白色大理石制成，提供大小两种尺寸。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211909U6sVeG4NxPR1HSwm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211909oS3EQ9jUXHMFBk2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211909eH6GsyuomOghcrav.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.284264\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211910RNUglJ8khQFVH2Cq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.050761\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hanger by  XYZ integrated architecture</h3><p>我们平日里常见的衣架，大多是三角结构，有着柔和圆角的挂钩，它满足了基本的功能性需求。但 XYZ integrated architecture 团队试图在其功能性的基础之上，加入一些充满想象力的趣味元素。</p><p>他们设计了一系列名为 Hanger 的衣架，这些由金属丝纽成各种形状的挂衣架像是一幅幅写意的艺术作品<b>，</b>采用不锈钢丝手工制作而成，它可能会在你挂衣服时制造一些小乐趣，不过看上去似乎也有些凌乱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211946ky5uAsdeNPHEMinr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.279951\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804022119462PCkRUEzmhbZNBce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.256724\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211947n7Q2tyIVSOAr9lh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.311736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211947TtBA0PcZvmkSw1Cr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.443765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211946cQ10vdBJiwfFUAG8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.319071\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211947IxWBNOR5nSquEi3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402211947VDTZtgEvQjX2ofAs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.094132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/xyz-integrated-architecture-03-30-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></p><h3>Filla Chair by Michele de Lucchi</h3><p>建筑师 Michele de Lucchi 与意大利座椅公司 Very Wood 合作，设计了一款名为 Filla 的座椅。这是一把轻质灰木座椅，向上延展的后腿支撑着两片巨大的“叶子”，这是设计师意在模仿树叶形状设计的分离式靠背，其圆润的边缘让人联想到树木的年轮。用于靠背的木材可以是天然木材，也可以人工染色，创造优雅而不规则的年轮般的曲线，仿佛这把椅子也可以像树木一样生长、老去。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212026b4s7aZE0AfLV6whY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771394\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212026NaE1bHZClx0kPIX8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212026zX7Vbx5MjyTRgYGA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212026jRkUSIyBKMa1VqQf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803178\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212027IBDlrb9RUzt64mNw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Le Morandine by Sonia Pedrazzini</h3><p>乔治·莫兰迪是意大利著名的油画家、版画家，他画的关于瓶罐器皿的油画就超过 1000 张，在其画作中，这些静物成为抽象的符号。他的作品也给了不少设计师灵感。</p><p>继之前推出以莫兰迪作品为灵感的限量系列蜡烛后，设计师 Sonia Pedrazzini 又将莫兰迪画作中的静物转化为一系列真实的陶瓷花瓶，并将其命名为 Le Morandine。Sonia Pedrazzini 特意将这些花瓶设计成莫兰迪作品中特有的配色，搭配类似粉笔质感的哑光外观，与莫兰迪日常绘画时使用的静物模型十分相似。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049Q7EF56xfuHJMKwGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679707\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049DUR8ezVSiyvh9PX0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804022120490fF2bNynQG3g4ark.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663814\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049dylI2Ykc7tb4ufAD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504890\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049niepjZHUlw78Ndb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049rJk6YZRqbPO4wClx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212049PsR4KDc1ZBbE3VAk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://katarinadileva.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">katarina di leva</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Verde Mirror by Rikke Frost for Woud</h3><p>2015 年成立的丹麦设计品牌 Woud，集结了不少北欧设计师佳作，包括 M-S-D-S, Poiat, Steffen Juul, Mikko Laakkonen, Philip Bro, Leonard Aldenhoff 等，创作出融合简约美学与实用功能的居家产品。</p><p>这款名为 Verde 的镜子是其代表作之一，出自设计师 Rikke Frost 之手。它的结构很简单，一个基本款圆形镜面，下方是一个轻薄的金属几何延长杆，其设计受到 1950 年代金属家具的启发。</p><p>镜面后方有一个隐藏的收纳架，可以用来摆放洗浴产品或是化妆品，下方的金属杆可以用于悬挂毛巾等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212128u2B9Lrkcn81GvYiX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.258750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018040221212837NETzdoPnFDsHuW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.483750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212128dSHmyVMAUf0J57Xz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.277500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212128pITvNHxBo8nYbiu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180402212128LE3HNgCjcvP0KWan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.woud.dk/verde-mirror/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Woud</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}